{"tid":2110714,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股票代碼與Tsla太相近  生物科技公司Tiziana順勢爆升","createTime":"2020-07-16T05:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T11:57:41.000Z","uid":28765,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7fdc6176781ea62d5f72b763cb7200338fa5646c","tid":2110714,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"巴隆週刊》（Barron's）報導指出，Tiziana股價（TLSA）週三一度衝上盤中歷史新高，明顯是投資者將其代碼與特斯拉（TSLA）搞混，更有趣的是，Tiziana股價在過去1個月裡飆漲47%，特斯拉股價也上漲56%；此外，Tiziana股價今年迄今上漲219%，特斯拉股價則上漲270%。<br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》說法，Tiziana作為1家生技公司，不僅沒有銷售數字，也沒有1個分析師追蹤這檔股票，今年年初時，Tiziana市值僅不到7500萬美元，直到今年武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情爆發，Tiziana才開始有些動作出現，像是宣佈在療法開發方面的合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n《巴隆週刊》指出，像這樣將「TLSA」與「TSLA」搞混的案例並非今年首見，如「Zoom Technologies」今年稍早就被不少投資人誤當成視訊會議服務公司「Zoom Video」，由於Zoom Video股價在疫情期間一飛衝天，「Zoom Technologies」也因名字相近，意外搭上這股順風車，當時美國證券交易委員會（SEC）一度出面暫停Zoom Technologies的股票交易，防止混亂情況升級。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3230281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3230281&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3ze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=c528b0c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3230281&h=dbddc4a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3230281</a>"},{"pid":"03246d68815a79816b8df9009cebf3186cdc6bc0","tid":2110714,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:02:56.000Z","msg":"好似之前隻ZM咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef3b859b5361ddc6723e14b728b23f2459e2fc4","tid":2110714,"uid":54545,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:05:58.000Z","msg":"𠵱個世界真係咁on9嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5d31319fbcd5f19bbcdeb999ceb1e787b76281